query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1 a1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 5
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('algorithm',
'c#',
'c++',
'java',
'performance')
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 10
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('codereview')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id group by t1.name;
